            "title": "電動化戰略大轉向 本田汽車預計全年虧損 美股盤前一度挫逾8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"電動化戰略大轉向 本田汽車預計全年虧損 美股盤前一度挫逾8%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"689\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wHJARJgB5FAvA3meAo72jw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4OQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/1816ac60-1e1d-11f1-bb7e-84df0fe55eb7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">電動化戰略大轉向 本田汽車預計全年虧損 美股盤前一度挫逾8%</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
